        dc:description           "FIGURES 6–15. Body of species of Nogueirapis Moure, 1953 in lateral and dorsal view respectively for each species. 6, 7: Nogueirapis minor (Moure & Camargo, 1982). 8, 9: Nogueirapis mirandula (Cockerell, 1917). 10, 11: Nogueirapis butteli (Friese, 1900). 12, 13: Nogueirapis batistai sp. nov. 14, 15: Nogueirapis rosariae sp. nov. Scale bar: 1 mm." ;
